{"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CarouselViewController","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Getting-Started","doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Carousel-Setup","doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Standalone-View-Controllers","doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Theming-and-Customization"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CarouselViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" serves as the central UI component of the SDK, offering"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"users seamless navigation between multiple content sources such as replica (PDF-based)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"editions, feed (HTML\/PDF) editions, archives, bookmarked content, and downloaded editions."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The interface supports two levels of paging, sections and subsections, with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"horizontal ribbons, allowing quick and intuitive browsing through publications.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The view controller can be configured via a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselConfiguration","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Utilize this configuration to align the visual presentation, navigation behavior,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"theming, branding, and various delegate interactions (e.g., sharing, paywalls,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"advertisements, and media playback)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The content in the carousel can be:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A Responsive feed edition archive."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A Replica PDF archive."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A Dynamic archive loaded from an app shortcode.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Local bookmarks."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Local downloads.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Usage","level":2,"anchor":"Usage","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The recommended approach uses a ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"dynamic archive"}]},{"text":" that loads content from a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"shortcode configured in the PageSuite portal:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let globalConfig = GlobalConfiguration(","    apiKey: \"YOUR_API_KEY\",","    accountGUID: \"YOUR_ACCOUNT_GUID\"",")","","let carousel = CarouselViewController(","    globalConfig: globalConfig,","    sections: [","        .dynamicArchive(\"Editions\", shortcode: \"YOUR_SHORTCODE\")","    ]",")","","present(carousel, animated: true)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can also configure sections manually to combine multiple content sources:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let carousel = CarouselViewController(","    globalConfig: globalConfig,","    sections: [","        .subsections(\"Editions\", [","            .init(name: \"Daily\", type: .feedArchive(guid: \"DAILY_GUID\")),","            .init(name: \"Weekend\", type: .feedArchive(guid: \"WEEKEND_GUID\"))","        ]),","        .section(.init(name: \"Bookmarks\", type: .bookmarks(type: .all))),","        .section(.init(name: \"Downloads\", type: .downloads(type: .all)))","    ]",")"]},{"style":"tip","type":"aside","name":"Tip","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CarouselViewController"},{"text":" calls ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PSReader.initialize(apiKey:)"},{"text":" internally.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For faster launches, call it earlier in your app lifecycle (e.g., in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application(_:didFinishLaunchingWithOptions:)"},{"text":").","type":"text"}]}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Getting-Started","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Carousel-Setup","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/GlobalConfiguration","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselConfiguration","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI